00:17:17.286 --> 00:17:20.956  position:5.00%,start  align:start size:90.00%  line:84.33% 
made me feel like it did
when you were with Mom.

413
00:17:21.040 --> 00:17:25.085  position:5.00%,start  align:start size:90.00%  line:84.33% 
