414
00:17:25.169 --> 00:17:27.713  position:30.00%,start  align:start size:65.00%  line:79.00% 
Okay. Well,
that’s how I used to feel
with you and Dad.

415
00:17:28.464 --> 00:17:29.756  position:20.00%,start  align:start size:75.00%  line:89.67% 
I know.

416
00:17:29.840 --> 00:17:33.970  position:5.00%,start  align:start size:90.00%  line:84.33% 
I know. We-We chose teams,
even during the divorce, and–

417
00:17:36.138 --> 00:17:41.810  position:5.00%,start  align:start size:90.00%  line:79.00% 
Okay, the last couple of years,
you and I have been
our own team, you know?

418
00:17:41.894 --> 00:17:44.354  position:5.00%,start  align:start size:90.00%  line:84.33% 
And I don’t want that
to go away.

419
00:17:44.438 --> 00:17:49.109  position:5.00%,start  align:start size:35.00%  line:70.50% 
So, I guess I just felt
a little left out today.

420
00:17:44.438 --> 00:17:49.109  position:65.00%,start  align:start size:15.00%  line:89.66% 
Shut up.

421
00:17:49.193 --> 00:17:51.111  position:60.00%,start  align:start size:35.00%  line:89.67% 
[ Sniffles ]

422
00:17:51.195 --> 00:17:53.655  position:5.00%,start  align:start size:90.00%  line:84.33% 
Okay, can you two
try hugging a box...

423
00:17:53.739 --> 00:17:56.867  position:5.00%,start  align:start size:90.00%  line:79.00% 
so that your poor mother
doesn’t have to do
all the hard work?

424
00:17:56.951 --> 00:17:59.494  position:5.00%,start  align:start size:90.00%  line:84.33% 
I am sorry, Gloria,
about all the mom stuff today.

425
00:17:59.578 --> 00:18:03.582  position:5.00%,start  align:start size:90.00%  line:79.00% 
