that you like Mitchell
better than me.

426
00:18:03.666 --> 00:18:05.626  position:65.00%,start  align:start size:30.00%  line:84.33% 
I do like Mitchell
better than you.

427
00:18:05.710 --> 00:18:06.752  position:45.00%,start  align:start size:50.00%  line:89.67% 
Why?

428
00:18:06.836 --> 00:18:08.128  position:75.00%,start  align:start size:20.00%  line:89.67% 
<i>Ay,</i> please.

429
00:18:08.212 --> 00:18:09.796  position:65.00%,start  align:start size:30.00%  line:84.33% 
Are you going to
honestly tell me...

430
00:18:09.880 --> 00:18:12.132  position:60.00%,start  align:start size:35.00%  line:79.00% 
that I’m
your favorite person
in this family?

431
00:18:12.216 --> 00:18:15.093  position:55.00%,start  align:start size:40.00%  line:79.00% 
I’m not even
your favorite Colombian
in this family.

432
00:18:15.177 --> 00:18:18.347  position:55.00%,start  align:start size:40.00%  line:79.00% 
I would love
to get closer to you.
You have my number.

433
00:18:18.431 --> 00:18:22.059  position:60.00%,start  align:start size:35.00%  line:84.33% 
But call me quickly,
because I book up.

434
00:18:23.728 --> 00:18:25.229  position:60.00%,start  align:start size:35.00%  line:89.67% 
You never saw me!

435
00:18:29.066 --> 00:18:31.485  position:70.00%,start  align:start size:25.00%  line:79.00% 
There you are.
I really need to
talk to you.

436
00:18:31.569 --> 00:18:33.862  position:10.00%,start  align:start size:30.00%  line:69.06% 
You really don’t.

437
00:18:31.569 --> 00:18:33.862  position:70.00%,start  align:start size:25.00%  line:84.23% 
Jay, please.
It’s about work.

438
00:18:33.946 --> 00:18:35.614  position:55.00%,start  align:start size:40.00%  line:84.33% 
I got a text
during your massage.

439
00:18:35.698 --> 00:18:37.616  position:65.00%,start  align:start size:30.00%  line:79.00% 
I’ve been offered
a partnership
in a new agency.

440
00:18:38.451 --> 00:18:39.535  position:20.00%,start  align:start size:75.00%  line:89.67% 
Oh.

441
00:18:41.120 --> 00:18:43.580  position:15.00%,start  align:start size:25.00%  line:75.93% 
Good for you.

442
00:18:41.120 --> 00:18:43.580  position:60.00%,start  align:start size:35.00%  line:89.66% 
Well, I’m not so sure.

443
00:18:43.664 --> 00:18:47.626  position:55.00%,start  align:start size:40.00%  line:79.00% 
