444
00:18:47.710 --> 00:18:50.254  position:30.00%,start  align:start size:65.00%  line:79.00% 
I have three kids,
and at least one of ’em’s
going to college.

445
00:18:50.338 --> 00:18:52.547  position:60.00%,start  align:start size:35.00%  line:84.33% 
Worst-case scenario,
they all go.

446
00:18:52.631 --> 00:18:54.216  position:5.00%,start  align:start size:90.00%  line:89.67% 
Well, what does Claire think?

447
00:18:55.551 --> 00:18:58.345  position:60.00%,start  align:start size:35.00%  line:79.00% 
I haven’t told her yet.
I wanted to
talk to you first.

448
00:18:58.429 --> 00:18:59.930  position:65.00%,start  align:start size:30.00%  line:89.67% 
You’ve done this.

449
00:19:00.014 --> 00:19:03.475  position:5.00%,start  align:start size:90.00%  line:84.33% 
