only really one question.

450
00:19:03.559 --> 00:19:05.227  position:50.00%,start  align:start size:45.00%  line:84.33% 
Whether I’m ready
to run my own company?

451
00:19:05.311 --> 00:19:08.480  position:5.00%,start  align:start size:90.00%  line:84.33% 
Nah, you’re great with people.
We know you’re a good salesman.

452
00:19:08.564 --> 00:19:11.400  position:5.00%,start  align:start size:90.00%  line:84.33% 
