a good living in tough times.

453
00:19:11.484 --> 00:19:12.985  position:60.00%,start  align:start size:35.00%  line:84.33% 
Then what?
Is this the right time?

454
00:19:13.069 --> 00:19:15.153  position:5.00%,start  align:start size:90.00%  line:84.33% 
Never a perfect time.
House could burn down tomorrow.

455
00:19:15.237 --> 00:19:18.741  position:5.00%,start  align:start size:90.00%  line:89.67% 
Question is, do you want this?

456
00:19:20.076 --> 00:19:22.661  position:60.00%,start  align:start size:35.00%  line:84.33% 
Yeah.
Yeah, I really want it.

457
00:19:22.745 --> 00:19:24.997  position:5.00%,start  align:start size:90.00%  line:89.67% 
Then gamble on yourself.

458
00:19:26.415 --> 00:19:28.334  position:10.00%,start  align:start size:85.00%  line:89.67% 
I’d gamble on you.

459
00:19:30.419 --> 00:19:31.420  position:35.00%,start  align:start size:60.00%  line:89.67% 
I’m gonna do it.

460
00:19:31.504 --> 00:19:33.171  position:15.00%,start  align:start size:25.00%  line:75.93% 
There you go.

461
00:19:31.504 --> 00:19:33.171  position:75.00%,start  align:start size:20.00%  line:89.66% 
[ Chuckles ]

462
00:19:33.255 --> 00:19:35.007  position:70.00%,start  align:start size:25.00%  line:89.67% 
Thanks, Jay.

463
00:19:35.091 --> 00:19:37.301  position:25.00%,start  align:start size:70.00%  line:79.00% 
Hey, look,
I know you were reluctant
to get that massage,

464
00:19:37.385 --> 00:19:39.929  position:5.00%,start  align:start size:90.00%  line:84.33% 
but I think we can both agree
it had a happy ending.

465
00:19:41.722 --> 00:19:43.181  position:30.00%,start  align:start size:65.00%  line:89.67% 
Please don’t say that.

466
00:19:43.265 --> 00:19:46.601  position:5.00%,start  align:start size:90.00%  line:84.33% 
If I could only save
one possession in a fire–

467
