<i>Probably my first set</i>
<i>of golf clubs.</i>
<i>My old man gave ’em to me.</i>

468
00:19:50.147 --> 00:19:52.024  position:5.00%,start  align:start size:25.00%  line:75.93% 
Here, I got it.

469
00:19:50.147 --> 00:19:52.024  position:60.00%,start  align:start size:20.00%  line:89.66% 
No, no, no.

470
00:19:53.776 --> 00:19:56.737  position:5.00%,start  align:start size:90.00%  line:79.00% 
