<i>Lily’s adoption papers.</i>

472
00:19:59.532 --> 00:20:01.450  position:5.00%,start  align:start size:90.00%  line:79.00% 
<i>[ Cameron ]</i>
<i>I was gonna say</i>
<i>adoption papers.</i>

473
00:20:01.534 --> 00:20:04.995  position:5.00%,start  align:start size:90.00%  line:84.33% 
<i>So I guess then I would say</i>
<i>my mama’s recipe book.</i>

474
00:20:06.372 --> 00:20:08.707  position:5.00%,start  align:start size:90.00%  line:84.33% 
<i>[ Phil ]</i>
<i>All our family photos...</i>

475
00:20:08.791 --> 00:20:11.210  position:5.00%,start  align:start size:90.00%  line:84.33% 
<i>which I keep on my iPad,</i>
<i>so my iPad.</i>

476
00:20:12.795 --> 00:20:15.088  position:5.00%,start  align:start size:90.00%  line:79.00% 
<i>[ Claire ]</i>
