480
00:20:20.469 --> 00:20:23.013  position:20.00%,start  align:start size:10.00%  line:69.06% 
Yeah.

481
00:20:20.469 --> 00:20:23.013  position:40.00%,start  align:start size:15.00%  line:84.23% 
