Boo!

483
00:20:23.097 --> 00:20:25.724  position:40.00%,start  align:start size:20.00%  line:89.66% 
[ Chuckles ]

484
00:20:26.976 --> 00:20:27.977  position:20.00%,start  align:start size:75.00%  line:89.67% 
