490
00:20:36.277 --> 00:20:38.737  position:5.00%,start  align:start size:10.00%  line:18.74% 
Shh.

491
00:20:38.821 --> 00:20:40.030  position:5.00%,start  align:start size:90.00%  line:5.00% 
