496
00:20:46.203 --> 00:20:47.579  position:5.00%,start  align:start size:10.00%  line:18.74% 
Shh!

497
00:20:47.663 --> 00:20:48.914  position:60.00%,start  align:start size:35.00%  line:5.00% 
