503
00:20:57.840 --> 00:20:59.300  position:5.00%,start  align:start size:90.00%  line:5.00% 
I’m going back to bed.

504
00:21:01.177 --> 00:21:02.219  position:30.00%,start  align:start size:65.00%  line:5.00% 
